      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "AUTUMN BOY (1) was safely held on debut after settling well back when seventh (30.74) at this track over 520m. Drops down the inside box this time. This looks easier and expected to improve sharply. OUR LITTLE SUZIE (2) has been hard to follow lately, running eighth (19.11) last time but prior to that ran very well when placed at this track. Expecting significant improvement this line-up. SAM'S VENDETTA (4) has a solid record despite not breaking through for a win in 30 starts. Was below best last time when missed the frame finishing seventh (19.07) at this track. Key runner who gets his chance to atone. HEY BARBIE GIRL (7) is a Christine Proctor-trained newcomer by Bernardo out of Rose Of Lachlan. Start all important and will need some luck getting across from the wide draw. Can sneak into the frame with the right run.",
